 《鳄鱼邓迪》中的鳄鱼伯特去世，享年 90 岁https://www.nme.com/news/film/burt-the-crocodile-from-crocodile-dundee-has-died-age-90-3824515?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=burt-the-crocodile-from-鳄鱼邓迪已去世，年龄 90 岁Aneesa AhmedMon, 23 Dec 2024 15:13:17 +0000 Film NewsNewsAustralia https://www.nme.com/?p=3824515 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="保罗·霍根在《鳄鱼邓迪》中。图片来源：派拉蒙影业" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “伯特确实是独一无二的。他不仅仅是一条鳄鱼；他是一种自然力量，提醒人们这些令人难以置信的生物的力量和威严。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/burt-the-crocodile-from-crocodile-dundee-has-died-age-90-3824515">《鳄鱼邓迪》中的鳄鱼伯特去世，享年 90 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="保罗·霍根在《鳄鱼邓迪》中。图片来源：派拉蒙影业" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>鳄鱼伯特 (Burt the Crocodile) 于 1986 年与保罗·霍根 (Paul Hogan) 一起主演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/australia">澳大利亚</a>喜剧<em>《鳄鱼邓迪》(Crocodile Dundee</em> )，现已去世，享年 90 岁。</p><p>澳大利亚达尔文市鳄鱼龙湾 (Crocosaurus Cove) 水族馆和展览馆证实了这一消息，伯特自 2008 年以来一直居住在那里，成为鳄鱼教育的“大使”。</p><p> “伯特在周末平静地去世了，估计已经90多岁了，标志着一个令人难以置信的时代的结束，”鳄鱼湾在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DD5hifoSWYj/?hl=en&amp;img_index=2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">社交媒体</a>上写道。</p><p> “伯特的人生故事充满了力量、韧性和与北端地区一样大胆的个性。伯特于 20 世纪 80 年代在雷诺兹河捕获，成为世界上最受认可的鳄鱼之一，出现在<em>鳄鱼邓迪</em>，并帮助塑造了澳大利亚作为一个拥有崎岖自然美景和令人惊叹的野生动物的土地的形象。”</p><p>后来写道：“伯特确实是独一无二的。他不仅仅是一条鳄鱼；他是一条鳄鱼。他是自然的力量，提醒人们这些令人难以置信的生物的力量和威严。虽然他的性格可能具有挑战性，但这也让他如此令人难忘，深受与他共事的人和多年来拜访他的数千人的喜爱。来自世界各地的游客都惊叹于它令人印象深刻的体型和威严的存在，尤其是在喂食的时候。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DD5hifoSWYj/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; 